
Please refer to the article at...

http://danpburke.blogspot.com.au/2012/11/one-shiny-dragon.html

...for a full explanation.

WASD keys move around.
Holding Left Mouse aims the camera.
ESC quits.
F11 toggles Fullscreen.

This requires an Nvidia card. It uses Nvidia extensions.
You'll need at least a gt240 AFAIK, but you want at least a GTX560.
1Gb of VRAM is mandatory. 

It's a tech demo, don't expect it to work fast or at all.

-Dan


